assertion.name: Ethics
assertion.value: This study used DNA sequence data from the UK Biobank, which has approval from the North West Multi-centre Research Ethics Committee (MREC) as a Research Tissue Bank (RTB) approval (approval number: 11/NW/0382). No specific ethical approval was required for DNA methylation data in this study, which is downloaded from GEO publicly available database with access number GSE42861.
